chapters.title: Chapter 3:  A Fan of Colors
chapters.info:
Joline Maza,
      p. 146 (164)â€”Aes Sedai of the Green Ajah.  She was a Sitter for the Green,
      appointed after one of the Green's sitters left for Salidar.
      Elaida asked her to resign her position after only
      weeks and sent her to Ebou Dar to meet with
      Queen Tylin of Altara.  She has two Warders named
      Blaeric and Fen.
      See also
      Mizar, Fen;
      Negina, Blaeric.
